_:Nbb5409f4b81e4a7bac18664a1d21c4a2 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Shabana Mahmood was appointed Secretary of State for the Home Department on 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Lord Chancellor and Secretary of State for Justice between 5 July 2024 and 5 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Birmingham Ladywood in July 2024.</p>\n" .
